data.description: Welcome home to this adorable Cottage with two bedrooms, one full bathroom and one - half bathroom on a beautiful corner lot.  Enter into a spacious Living Room with a Fireplace, great for entertaining.  Located off of the Living Room is a Formal Dining Room with corner built-in Hutches.  There is office space/ bonus room/ or third bedroom also located off of the Living Room.  The Kitchen has black pearl granite counter tops and boast of great cabinet space and adjacent to the laundry room.  Located in the heart of Walterboro Business District and Historical area, walking distance to downtown Walterboro and the Wildlife Sanctuary and Wildlife Center.  This home is being sold AS - IS.
